      "span_text": "All substrates were then coated with Polyethyleneimine (PEI, Sigma-Aldrich, Belgium)  , by soaking their surface in a 0.1% PEI solution (w/v) overnight, and afterwards rinsed in deionized water and left drying at room temperature, prior to cell seeding."
